diary_text = "I spent the night hiding in the jungle. Every sound made me jump. I found some supplies in an old camp, but the enemy is everywhere.

I found a map on a dead soldier. I am deeper in enemy territory than I thought.

No more hiding. I have to fight my way through the ruins. I am not stopping now."

